  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to determine if the use of atorvastatin (Lipitor), a member of the HMG
      coA reductase inhibitor class of drugs referred to as statins, will reduce inflammatory
      responses and deep vein thrombosis formation when given in high doses in the perioperative
      period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
