  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  gynecologic tumor scheduled for resection

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  prior reaction to statins

          -  renal insufficiency

          -  liver disease

          -  h/o alcoholism

          -  prior h/o DVT or hypercoagulability

          -  concurrent medications that significantly affect cytochrome P450 3A4

          -  breast feeding or pregnancy
      </textblock>
